text: From Justin to Kelly is a 2003 American romantic musical comedy movie. It was directed by Robert Iscove. Actors include Kelly Clarkson, Justin Guarini, Katherine Bailess, and Brian Dietzen. It was distributed by 20th Century Fox. The movie was nominated for 8 Golden Raspberry Awards in 2004. ==Other websites== * * * * Category:2003 romantic comedy movies Category:2003 musical movies Category:American musical comedy movies Category:American romantic comedy movies
